data.description: Welcome to this exquisite home, boasting just six years of age! Nestled mere minutes from Historic Downtown Leesburg, yet cocooned in serene tranquility within the heart of Loudoun County, this move-in-ready marvel awaits. Boasting 4 bedrooms and 3.5 baths, with a versatile basement room primed for customization as an additional bedroom, this residence exudes both elegance and practicality.  Step through the threshold, and an immediate sense of belonging envelops you. The grandeur of the tall, light-filled 2-story foyer sets the tone, adorned with meticulous details such as crown molding, soaring ceilings, and a striking stone fireplace in the great room, complemented by expansive windows ushering in abundant natural light.  The kitchen stands as a testament to culinary delight, featuring resplendent cabinetry, Granite countertops, a walk-in pantry, an expansive island housing a sink and dishwasher, and gleaming stainless-steel appliances. A capacious mudroom, replete with generous closet space for backpacks and shoes, seamlessly connects to the garage, ensuring organizational bliss.  Hardwood flooring, an embodiment of sophistication, graces the main level, including a versatile office/flex space, great room with plenty of space for the entire family to enjoy eating in the breakfast room. Ascend to the upper level to discover four bedrooms, each adorned with brand new carpet. Bathrooms exude opulence, boasting dual vanities, a luxurious soaking tub in the primary bath, and a capacious walk-in closet catering to all wardrobe needs.  Descending to the lower level unveils a sprawling recreation room, complete with pre-installed brackets for your big screen tv to help with your entertainment needs. Step outside to an enchanting stone patio, an idyllic backdrop for gatherings or quiet moments with loved ones. Additional amenities include a full bath and a separate den/office, offering the potential for a fifth bedroom.  Outside, a meticulously landscaped, fenced backyard awaits, complete with a children's play gym—an oasis crafted with over $40,000 worth of enhancements, ensuring safety for pets and peace of mind for homeowners. Conveniently situated with easy access to major thoroughfares (15, 7, Greenway), and adorned with fresh paint and new carpeting, this rare gem in Loudoun County epitomizes the epitome of modern luxury living.
